efer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":63,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI4pmn2rfrkwMVGIO6AB00qzklSMGgjN6jjt30bsoBBH5iEcM=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWg3X1U2SlR0V3RKNjFtOGo3TXJBUzduTEVlZ3xBQ3Jtc0trdVozN2t4ZzNOcEg0M2ZUUkRXWUJzQktZVTR4YTloTll1NFBDbDFYOGl5TklXR0FPTWVYVFN3T1plcmpmQXJLT0Z5RW9ndmZ2NEgxS2lRdEJvXzFpUjloa0ktcTlmelhPTjBneHhITGZjWVNyTHFuUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=bul0cjvDEEE","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWg3X1U2SlR0V3RKNjFtOGo3TXJBUzduTEVlZ3xBQ3Jtc0trdVozN2t4ZzNOcEg0M2ZUUkRXWUJzQktZVTR4YTloTll1NFBDbDFYOGl5TklXR0FPTWVYVFN3T1plcmpmQXJLT0Z5RW9ndmZ2NEgxS2lRdEJvXzFpUjloa0ktcTlmelhPTjBneHhITGZjWVNyTHFuUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=bul0cjvDEEE","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":175,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI4pmn2rfrkwMVGIO6AB00qzklSMGgjN6jjt30bsoBBH5iEcM=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbjYxNTZES2FCbmxxS1VQR3l5bDU2NEFCMVpyd3xBQ3Jtc0trNmZYcW1Rc25vMG15UFJPaE9sOEZONHV4UXhGTkJPeHRldnJzSnNkcnlaT0s1bDJnU0R2UU1DNkFSY3YxeXJ2c0NUQ3RnOXZmNzN